課程概述 Course Description
       本課程是供醫學檢驗生物技術學系學生學習醫學有關的微生物，它包括細菌學、黴菌學及病毒學，除講課授課外還包括實驗課，也利用電腦輔助教材，錄影帶、實際病例的問題解決方法，增加教學內容與效率，鼓勵學生透過討論來學習。本課程與醫學系的醫學微生物學類似，但針對醫技系學生在內容上做適度地修正 

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
    

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
11. Microbial classification & structure2. Microbial physiology   Lab: Understanding: Bacteria (Video)23. Microbial genetics & bacteriophage4. Sterilization, disinfection & antisepsis   Lab: Technique35. Mechanisms of bacterial pathogenesis6. Antibacterial agents & laboratory diagnosis of bacterial diseases   Lab: Gram stain & Simple stain47.  Staphylococcus, Streptococcus & Neisseria (I) Staphylococcus, Streptococcus & Neisseria (II)   Lab: Antibiotics: Misused miracles (Video)59. Corynebacterium, Listeria & ErysipelothrixPseudomonas & Legionella   Lab: Drug susceptibility & Action of chemical agents on bacteria611. EnterobacteriaceaeVibrio & Helicobacter   Lab: Characteristics of Streptococcus713.Pseudomonas & Legionella14.Exam. I (8:40-10:20 四樓實驗室)8Dermatophytoses & Subcutaneous mycosesBacillus, Clostridium & BacteroidesLab: Characteristics of StaphylococcusLaboratory diagnosis of N. gonorrhoeae917. Clostridium & Bacteroides   Lab: Identification of Enterobacteriaceae1018. Mycobacteria, Nocardia & ActinomycesSpirochetes & Mycoplasma   Lab: Anaerobic culture & Spore stain1120. Chlamydia & Rickettsia 21. Viral characterization and classification   Lab: Acid-Fast stain & Albert stain1222. Viral replication and viral genetics23. Mechanisms of viral pathogenesis12/3 Exam. II (AM 10:20-11:50 四樓實驗室)1324. Papillomaviruses, Polyomaviruses and Adenoviruses25. Poxviruses and Parvoviruses   Lab: Understanding: Viruses (Video)1426. Picornaviruses and Reoviruses27. Orthomyxoviruses and Paramyxoviruses   Lab: Bacteriophage plaque observation and count1528. Hepatitis viruses29. Herpesviruses   Lab: Polyhedrosis of the AcMNPV baculovirus1630. Coronaviruses, Noraviruses, Rhabdoviruses, Filoviruses and Bornaviruses1731. Togaviruses and Flaviviruses32. Bunyaviruses and Arenaviruses   Lab: Hemagglutination of parainfluenza virus1833. Retroviruses and Prion34. 1/14 Lab. Exam. (AM 8:30-10:00 四樓實驗室)         Final Exam. (AM 10:00-11:30 四樓實驗室) 

